events.name: Wake Forest Demon Deacons at Clemson Tigers

headlines.description: Deshaun Watson and Clemson enjoyed another big day and kept on track for the College Football Playoff with a 33-13 victory over Wake Forest on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Watson, No. 1 Clemson romp past Wake Forest

events.name: Charleston Southern Buccaneers at Alabama Crimson Tide

headlines.description: Cyrus Jones returned two punts for touchdowns and Derrick Henry scored twice as Alabama romped past Charleston Southern 56-6 on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jones, Henry help Bama top Charleston Southern

events.name: Michigan State Spartans at Ohio State Buckeyes

headlines.description: Michael Geiger kicked a 41-yard field goal as time expired and Connor Cook-less Michigan State ended Ohio State's 23-game winning streak.

video.headline: Late field goal gives Ohio State first loss of season

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (SC HOTN: Michigan State-Ohio State) 2015/11/21 ESHEET SC

headlines.shortLinkText: Spartans knock off Ohio State on last-second FG

events.name: Boston College Eagles at Notre Dame Fighting Irish

headlines.description: DeShone Kizer threw for two touchdowns -- and three interceptions -- on Saturday night as Notre Dame survived five turnovers to beat Boston College 19-16 at Fenway Park.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 4 Irish survive 5 TOs, beat BC at Fenway

events.name: Purdue Boilermakers at Iowa Hawkeyes

headlines.description: C.J. Beathard threw three touchdown passes, and Iowa clinched a share of the Big Ten West title and a spot in the league championship game with a 40-20 win over Purdue on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Iowa tops Purdue, clinches Big Ten West

events.name: Baylor Bears at Oklahoma State Cowboys

headlines.description: Backup quarterback Chris Johnson threw two touchdown passes and ran for a score, and Baylor beat previously unbeaten Oklahoma State to climb back into the College Football Playoff mix.
headlines.shortLinkText: CFP hopes flip as Baylor knocks off Oklahoma St.

events.name: TCU Horned Frogs at Oklahoma Sooners

headlines.description: Oklahoma's Steven Parker batted away Bram Kohlhausen's 2-point conversion attempt with less than a minute left and the seventh-ranked Sooners survived a late rally to beat TCU on Saturday.

video.headline: Oklahoma loses Mayfield in close win over TCU

headlines.shortLinkText: No. 18 TCU rally falls short to No. 7 Oklahoma

events.name: Florida Atlantic Owls at Florida Gators

headlines.description: Treon Harris' 13-yard touchdown pass to Jake McGee in overtime allowed Florida to avoid a huge upset and turn back Florida Atlantic 20-14 on Saturday.

video.headline: Florida survives OT scare from Florida Atlantic

headlines.shortLinkText: Florida withstands in-state Owls' upset effort

events.name: California Golden Bears at Stanford Cardinal

headlines.description: Christian McCaffrey ran around the Cal defense on a 49-yard TD catch and scored on a 98-yard kickoff return to help Stanford clinch a spot in the Pac-12 championship game with a Big Game win.

events.name: Chattanooga Mocs at Florida State Seminoles

Louisville Cardinals at Pittsburgh Panthers
